To build: Use latest Android Studio and Tools.

To set up emulator:
1) The broadcast address (configured in the Settings of the app) must be 10.0.2.255
2) A redirect must be configured in the emulator.
   a) Open the file ~/.emulator_console_auth_token and copy the contents
   b) Telnet into the emulator (the first emulator will be on port 5554)
   c) Authenticate with 'auth <paste-token-here>'
   d) redir add udp:5000:5000
   e) To confirm: redir list

